Package br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.port.outbound

package br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.port.outbound
This package contains the interfaces representing the operations that the OmniCommunicator needs to interact with the outside world. These interfaces are defined by the business logic and implemented by adapters.
